abstract: Convention holds that the Masters doesn't begin until the back nine Sunday. For the former Georgia Tech star Stewart Cink, it essentially ended on the front nine Saturday when he shot a five-over 41 on his way to an 81. He rebounded with a closing 69 to finish at eight over.

headline.main: Work Doesn't Stop for Cink After a Dismal Third Round
